 "description": "Aerial beings without the wish-granting of the fairy tales. They fight as Giants at −1 damage (1-11 per hit) and carry up to 6,000 Gold Pieces weight, walking or (briefly) flying. They create: sound food, drinkable drink, lasting soft goods and wooden things — but metal is short-lived (the harder, the shorter; Djinn-gold lasts a day) — and illusions that persist without concentration until touched or dispelled. They form a whirlwind 1\" base, 2\" top, 3\" high, otherwise as an Air Elemental's, and may go invisible or gaseous at will.",
